1. Install Homebrew Python2 and Python3
    brew install python@2
    brew install python
2. Install virtualenv
    pip install virtualenv
    pip3 install virtualenv
3. Set up virtual environments
    python2 -m virtualenv ~/py2_kernel
    python3 -m virtualenv ~/py3_kernel
4. Set up PDBPP
    mv .pdbrc.py ~
